overview: Destination X (2010) is a professional wrestling pay-per-view (PPV) event produced by the Total Nonstop Action Wrestling (TNA) promotion, which took place on March 21, 2010 at the TNA Impact! Zone in Orlando, Florida.[3] It was the sixth event under the Destination X chronology and the third event of the 2010 TNA PPV schedule.
title: TNA Destination X 2010
